name: Trickstar Shakunage
description: You can discard 1 "Trickstar" card, then target 1 "Trickstar" Link Monster in your GY: Special Summon it. You can only use this effect of "Trickstar Shakunage" once per turn. Each time a card(s) is banished from your opponent's GY, inflict 200 damage to them for each.
